title: #630 - Jerry Rocha
description:
Jerry Rocha, comedian and host of "The Ramble" podcast, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.

Joey's NETFLIX special as part of, "The Degenerates," is streaming now!

Jerry is recording his newest album this Thursday, November 1 at The Icehouse Comedy Club.
